{"type": "article", "id": 20270, "title": "只有八岁的他，拍出了这些大师级的风光片", "description": "虽然太明信片了一点，但是还是美的。", "date": "2016-01-06T07:00:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 31, "name": "英国"}, {"id": 153, "name": "摄影"}, {"id": 6657, "name": "风景"}, {"id": 21615, "name": "Oliver Andreas Jones"}], "category": 5, "author": 18, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 111, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021416417FZDlNTU1LkpIXJr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\">画面中这些美丽的景点是在英国完成拍摄的，<span style=\"text-align:left;\">图片看似出自一位专业的摄影师之手，但实则不然。</span>摄影师是英国年仅八岁的男孩Oliver Andreas Jones，<span style=\"text-align:left;\">小奥利弗目前还是一名小学生</span>。由于出色的拍摄能力，他最近刚被一家公司选作公司大使。这些取景点有的是在英伦乡下的侏罗纪海岸，有的是在英国国会大厦和地标建筑大本钟旁边。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214163701hpeUAQLfPri6VR.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"650\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021416386c2pA8Of1aobwqvr.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"718\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141638ELcqHbtdFvUyJXfP.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"494\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141639XPAn62SWgxfQqMa1.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"718\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141639No0DYXnxRb3aTSy1.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"718\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141640mdMHIJBwLa2hV49P.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"708\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141640M6B9LC1WVEs7iuzn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\">文中图片版权：Oliver Andreas Jones/Solent News Photo Agency</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t你还能在小奥利弗的 <a href=\"http://500px.com/oliverandreasjones\" target=\"_blank\">500px</a> 上看到更多的摄影作品\r\n</p>\n\n"}